(237, 'z', 'GRWY011', 'Cracked Wheat - Bulgur', 'Pre-Packed', 'products/GRWY011-L.jpg', 'jpg', NULL, NULL, 'Yara', 'Shelled Wheat', NULL, 'Whole grains, such as Shelled Wheat, are better than refined grains because of their fiber, vitamins and minerals contents. The use of the entire wheat kernel is very common in the Middle Eastern cuisine, and often replaces rice in a variety of specialty dishes. Whole wheat contains micronutrients like folic acid, magnesium and vitamin E, and with all the good things that it offers, it is easy to see why it makes up an important part of a healthy diet. Scientific evidence shows that the benefits of whole wheat really add up. Including whole wheat in your diet may lead to a healthier heart, help reduce the risk of certain types of cancer, play a role in diabetes management, help keep you regular and your digestive tract running smoothly.', '12-', '28 oz. (794g)', '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'YES', '3.49', '2.00', 'NO', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 56, NULL, 9),
