(239, 'z', 'GRWY015', 'Cracked Wheat - Bulgur', 'Pre-Packed', 'products/GRWY015-L.jpg', 'jpg', NULL, NULL, 'Yara', 'Freekeh - Green Wheat', NULL, 'Freekeh (pronounced “free-ka”) was discovered by accident over 2.000 years ago in the Middle East. Freekeh is a versatile super food packed with nutrition and health benefits. It is produced by harvesting grains while still soft, young and green, then parching roasting and drying. The process captures the grains at a state of peak taste and nutrition. Easy to prepare, delicious and aromatic. Freekeh has a superb toasted nutty flavor and is also incredibly versatile. It can be served as a side dish, mixed into salads, added into cake recipes or even formed into vegetarian burger patties. Mix made from green wheat and is a very popular dish in East Mediterranean.', '12-', '24 oz. (680g)', '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'YES', '4.99', '2.00', 'NO', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 56, NULL, 9);
