(324, 'z', 'DFRY009', 'Dried Fruits', 'Pre-Packed', 'products/DFRY009-L.jpg', 'jpg', NULL, NULL, 'Yara', 'Papaya', NULL, 'Dried papaya spears are made from fresh papaya fruit, they are full of tropical flavor and sweetness. As a fresh fruit papaya has a rich flavor, but dried papaya has even more intense flavor because drying concentrates its rich flavor. These are the perfect ingredient to add to cereals, nut mixes, salads, and desserts. Papayas are sweet and chewy and also a great source of Vitamin C.  Papayas grow in groups on tall trees, similar to coconut trees. They can weigh between one half a pound and up to 20 pounds. There are many varieties of Papayas and they are grown in many tropical countries. The exact origin of the Papaya is unknown but it is believed to be native to the Americas. Papaya is useful in aiding digestion because the enzymes of the fruit help to digest proteins, fats, and starches. The fiber of the fruit is helpful in streamlining the digestive tract. Ingredients: Papaya, sugar, citric acid, sulphur dioxide and artificial colors.', '12-', '8 oz. (227g)', '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'YES', '2.99', '0.80', 'NO', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 30, NULL, 9),
